chapters.title: What are some of the many titles the Spirit of Prophecy applies to the Remnant Church?
With whom did the name "Israel" originate? Genesis 32:24-29
Whose experience must we pass through before we enter heaven? [Jeremiah 30: 5-7]
According to the Apostle Paul whom are we wrestling with? [Ephesians 6:12]
Who was God's first denomination? Deuteronomy 7:6-8
In the days of the Apostle Paul whom did he liken as Israel? Romans 2:28-29
What were those people called who had defected from both Judaism and heathenism and had embraced the teachings of Jesus. Acts 11:26
If Ancient Israel did not keep their part of the covenant, what did God say would happen? Deuteronomy 30:15
If Ancient Israel rejected knowledge what would God do to them? [Hosea 4:6-7]
How much more time did God give the Jews to get right with Him? Daniel 9:24
